{"tid":673720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：飛天蠄蟧爆錯空屋 輕功爬外牆逃捕","createTime":"2018-05-22T05:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T06:26:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c244fd5663bba8aaf5fdfbffdadc8b03f7d4247a","tid":673720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398249&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7080070e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398249&h=30c000dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398249</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月22日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：飛天蠄蟧爆錯空屋<br />\n輕功爬外牆逃捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180522/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=1d1590ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ■兩賊由7樓爬過8樓，再爬上天台逃走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩名大懵孟加拉竊匪噚日潛入深水埗大南街一幢唐樓爆竊，竟然搵間空屋去偷，但搜掠時講嘢又唔識細細聲，結果驚動鄰居報警，並上演一幕警員圍捕飛天蠄蟧驚險場面，吸引唔少街坊圍觀，兩賊三爬兩撥上咗天台後分頭逃落街以為走得甩，但一名31歲賊仔被眼利差人認出，涉爆竊被捉返差館。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180522/large/a0902b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fa0902b.gif&h=939a974d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紫衫賊扮住客離開，被警員認出按地制服。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n施施然落樓被警認出<br />\n<br />\n話說噚日晏晝12點左右，大南街257號唐7樓一單位住客，聽到隔籬冇人住嘅空屋，竟然傳出南亞裔人士嘅嘈吵聲，疑有賊偷嘢，於是報警。警員上樓發現單位大門鎖頭被撬，拍門問吓，屋內其中一人扮住客開門，一見門外竟然係差人，馬上關門。<br />\n<br />\n兩個賊仔「冇碇匿」，只好冒險爬窗走，兩賊逃出窗外後遊走簷篷邊，「唔知佢哋係咪喺家鄉孟加拉爬樹爬得多」兩賊身手不凡，先由7樓爬上8樓，再由8樓爬到天台，其間嚇到樓下一班圍觀嘅街坊𠵱嘩鬼叫，有同鄉喺樓下用鄉下話不斷大嗌：「唔好咁啦，跌死你呀！」<br />\n<br />\n但兩賊唔知係聽唔到，抑或顧住逃走唔驚得咁多，只顧住向上爬，其間一個賊仔嘅手機跣手跌落街，「啪一聲」散開，嚇得途人心慌慌。<br />\n<br />\n兩賊爬上天台後失去蹤影，圍觀街坊以為事件告一段落，原來還有下半場，其中一名穿紫色衫賊仔逃上天台後，隨即爬至毗鄰261號唐樓天台，然後扮住客沿樓梯落街，再急步離開，但被3名便衣警員認出制服，穿橙衣同黨就走甩。<br />\n<br />\n全程目擊嘅街坊印度人Jacky話，被捕賊仔不時在深水埗「打躉」，對於賊人玩命逃避追捕，Jacky並不認同，「嗰度人來人往，跌落嚟壓死人，好危險！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：凌晨混戰　大埔FYY盲拳揼肥佬"},{"pid":"0cc5daa5522b12dbac58648503df6e7ec86bfaba","tid":673720,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/135232_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F135232_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=38e73794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9c029b59ee62e89c64a7cde9c841fc2bc84608ee","tid":673720,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2203870d9c910e2f80257f5450509e1d5dda58","tid":673720,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"衫都唔換 當人弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280f3add8e7ca105b386f49ea436464932e8c9e8","tid":673720,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c2203870d9c910e2f80257f5450509e1d5dda58","tid":673720,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"衫都唔換 當人弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"最危險嘅地方就係最安全嘅地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb685238a49edd2727c5d06c43f93973a499fbfd","tid":673720,"uid":123711,"like"